name: Princess Leia
Lore: 'Prominent leader in the struggling Alliance. Former member of the Imperial Senate. Beginning to discover her true heritage. Likes scoundrels.',
Text: 'May only deploy on Hoth or Cloud City. Adds 1 to power of anything she pilots. May deploy (on Hoth or Cloud City) or move as a ''react'' to same site as Han or Luke. Immune to attrition < 3.',
